description:
This welcoming apartment channels beautiful energy and allows guest to experience a harmonious and relaxing stay right in the HEART OF MIDTOWN EAST NYC! Vibrant neighborhood!

Only a few blocks from the main subway lines, and within a 12 minute walk to Grand Central, lets you reach main points of interest with ease.

Buddhism and Hinduism tradition inspired the unique and modern Mandalas home décor. Mandalas represent wholeness, health, connection, unity, harmony, and the cycle of life.

The Space

~APARTMENT ~
The apartment is in midtown east. The apartment is on a 2nd floor,1 flight up, elevator + wide staircase. Vibrant neighborhood; right next to supermarkets, delicious restaurants, all major banks, pharmacies, and Starbucks. 

~BEDROOM~    
•	Queen size bed with comfortable foam mattress (sleeps 2)
•	The Living room has a DayBed which is transformable into a double bed with 3 drawers for storage. Comfortable foam mattress (sleeps 2)
•	Electric-powered air mattress (sleeps 2)
~AMENITIES~
•	TV with Time Warner Cable in living room area
•	WiFi Super-fast 100 Mbps
•	Towels & Sheets
•	Shampoo, Conditioner, Body Soap
•	Steamer
•	Stove, Oven, Refrigerator, Microwave, Toaster
•	Washer and dryer in the building’s basement ( $1.25 for wash & $1.25 for dry)

~WELCOME PERKS~
•	Bottle of wine
•	Water Bottles
•	NYC Map

~CHECK IN- CHECK OUT
•	Check in is at 3PM 
•	Check out is at 12PM (NOON)


Getting around

Located in the heart of Midtown East, this apartment is a short walk from:

•	Rockefeller center and ice rink 10-minute walk away
•	Times Square- 20 minute walk away
•	Radio City Music Hall 14-minute walk away
•	Bloomingdales's 10-minute walk away
•	Bergdorf Goodman 18-minute walk away
•	Apple Store open 24hour 20-minute walk awa
•	Central Park 20-minute walk away
•	United Nations 5- minute walk away

~TRANSPORTATION~
•	Easy access to the New York City Subway System lines
•	Lexington Ave / 53 St. 4-minute walk away
E, M,6
•	Grand Central is just a 12-minute walk away
S, 4, 5, 6, 7
•	Lexington Ave / 53 St. 5-minute walk away
E, M
•	Bus Line M50 crosstown 
•	Times Square take the S train 1 stop
